Package: devtri
Type: Package
Title: Easily work with actuarial development triangles
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Andy", "Merlino", email = "andy.merlino@tychobra.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Andy Merlino <andy.merlino@tychobra.com>
Description: Work with actuarial development triangles to select loss development factors and
    use your selections to create simple reserve projections.
